4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners, allowing students to build their first ML models with no prior experience. The course spans 16 weeks, featuring three classes per week in small groups of up to 12 students. Participants will learn Python, SQL, and various data analysis tools, alongside practical experience with algorithms and real-life challenges. The course culminates in a recognized certificate, validating the skills acquired. Instruction is available in both English and Spanish.

